  <description>
    <p>Image Compare lets you inspect two images side by side or in a stacked view, making it easier to spot subtle visual changes and evaluate differences.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Side-by-side and stacked comparison</li>
      <li>Zoom and pan tools</li>
      <li>Create a heatmap of differences between two images</li>
      <li>Support for multiple image formats</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
